review: I have subscribed pro and it is more helpful and managing to do list.. However, i found sound option is not functioning during focus time and expecting different sound option for short break and long break and there is no pause option during focus time
If you tend to forget things, want to focus on a task n lots of such things then this app is a must have for you..enjoying it
This app will definitely help you to schedule your task and manage your day to day work
